# ShopFlow

Electron + React + MongoDB desktop app for single-company orders, billing, expenses, WhatsApp (Phase 4).

## Hard rules

- MongoDB runs in **main process only** — no separate Express/backend server
- Renderer uses **preload IPC** only — never import `mongodb` in renderer
- Follow **MVC**: Controller → Service → Repository
- IPC channels only in `shared/ipc-channels.ts`
- Check `docs/PHASES.md` before adding features — respect phase boundaries

## Docs

Read `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`, `docs/PROJECT-STRUCTURE.md`, `AGENTS.md` before structural changes.

## Current phase

Phase 0: foundation shell only — no orders/products/customers/WhatsApp business logic.
